PLAYER HELP
SPELL CRYSTAL
A spell crystal is a valuable object to magic users, allowing them to store mana for later use. They are created from quartz crystals with magic. Once you have one, you can ~CCOMuse~CHLP it to add your mana to it. Spell crystals are needed for magic staffs, or can be disjuncted to release the mana within.

~CCOMSee also: ~CREFcreate spell crystal
